{"tid":160926,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《陶傑開Talk》仇視大陸係必然　青年人不認同中國人身份","createTime":"2017-03-18T07:14:01.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T07:34:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"137f19420a3f4e64b10da44bbb4125a42ff537e4","tid":160926,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:14:01.000Z","msg":"《陶傑開Talk》仇視大陸係必然　青年人不認同中國人身份<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=auNOCuwS1MM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DauNOCuwS1MM&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d8a95cdd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=auNOCuwS1MM</a><br />\n<br />\nNextplus 壹週Plus <br />\nNextplus 壹週Plus<br />\nSubscribed101,646<br />\n Add to   Share  More<br />\n35,057 views<br />\n 121  18<br />\nPublished on Jul 3, 2016<br />\n現在各走極端：中國發現鬧大了，張德江來香港轉行所謂的寬鬆溫和語調，邀請民主派見面。但早知如此，又何必當初？十多年前你跟民主派坐下好好談，釋放一點善意空間，甚或至兩年前，尚有機會，政改方案不要做得那麼絕，讓年輕人在一個講道理的公平環境下，相信可以用選票改善現狀，就不會搞成今日之田地。<br />\n<br />\n想不到命運作弄中共與民主派。有一天，這對死敵，發現彼此都變成香港年輕人，即所謂「激進本土派」的敵人。很諷刺的是，今日如果司徒華在生，在香港的大學論壇出現，同台者是梁振英，兩人招惹到的喝倒采之聲，到底梁振英高於司徒華幾多分貝？<br />\n<br />\n這個令人哭笑不得的問題，令我不敢想像。這是一個混亂的世代，但再亂，只要堅持常識、是非，還加上與生俱來的一點良心，我相信，選擇做人還是做豬狗，應該還不算太難。<br />\n<br />\n採訪：艾馬<br />\n攝影：金文<br />\n<br />\n壹週Plus : <a href=\"http://hk.next.nextmedia.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=d8ddb278\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.next.nextmedia.com&h=8070474f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.next.nextmedia.com</a><br />\n即 like 壹週Plus fb : <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinef...\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnextmagazinef...&d=JxnAwUrH%2B1qYxVTFfur%2BVpUWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=7f6fbb1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.facebook.com/nextmagazinef...</a><br />\nCategory<br />\nNews &amp; Politics<br />\nLicense<br />\nStandard YouTube License"},{"pid":"b34530019b0517e3dabdc53a3151ba0e4392fe9b","tid":160926,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:15:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fa47f9eecc2881c8d68cc94f67fb1d95637fe6c","tid":160926,"uid":61462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T07:34:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}